      <title>Hindenburg 与印度监管机构的争执加剧，Adani 股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/adani-stocks-drop-as-hindenburg-row-with-india-regulator-worsens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[兴登堡研究公司 (Hindenburg Research) 指责印度市场监管机构负责人存在利益冲突，阻碍了对这家美国卖空者指控该企业集团存在操纵和欺诈行为的彻底调查，随后阿达尼集团 (Adani Group) 股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/adani-stocks-drop-as-hindenburg-row-with-india-regulator-worsens</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 04:20:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
